and on Envelop VR, which was a desktop VR platform.

12
00:00:41,747 --> 00:00:44,269
Most of my career has been focused on gameplay

13
00:00:44,349 --> 00:00:46,690
and interaction design, especially features

14
00:00:46,770 --> 00:00:48,851
that are highly physical and tactile.

15
00:00:49,571 --> 00:00:51,953
But I've also worked on everything from systems design

16
00:00:52,013 --> 00:00:53,173
to engine architecture.

17
00:00:53,854 --> 00:00:56,315
I'm sure any indie devs listening are familiar

18
00:00:56,355 --> 00:00:57,756
with wearing lots of different hats.

19
00:00:59,057 --> 00:01:01,678
And I would like to overhear a gameplay programmer

20
00:01:01,738 --> 00:01:02,318
in a system era.

21
