before making the jump to PC and console.

24
00:01:09,877 --> 00:01:10,938
In addition to programming,

25
00:01:11,198 --> 00:01:13,739
I also have a design background that's been part of my work.

26
00:01:14,559 --> 00:01:17,760
I've often worked in UI and UX and large gameplay systems.

27
